    "You should consult a qualified professional.\"",
    "Later, the same user asks about medical symptoms.",
    "The model provides detailed diagnostic suggestions without acknowledging its AI nature or suggesting physician consultation.",
    "Having observed the model disclose limitations for financial advice, the user may reasonably trust the model's confident medical guidance, assuming it reflects similarly qualified expertise.This pattern is analogous to the Gell-Mann Amnesia effect: people recognize errors or unreliability in domains they know well but trust the same source's information in unfamiliar domains.",
